    <section id="id18854285">
      <title>ABOUT CREEPY STORIES</title>
      <para id="id19774981">We all have things that give us the creeps - things that make us get goose bumps or want to hide under our blankies. They could be sounds or spiders or smells or sights. We all have fears and phobias. </para>
      <section id="id16867126">
        <title>Activity 1</title>
        <para id="para-id16867126">
