      <section id="id19094817">
        <title>To listen for information and identify the main theme [LO 1.6]</title>
        <list id="id18709002" list-type="bulleted">
          <item>Listen to the well-known poem by Allan Ahlberg, read to you by your educator, and then identify his three fears. </item>
          <item>Listen again and then identify his plan of action in a brave effort to ward off each fear.</item>
        </list>
